\id 3JN - Mbula NT with Gen, Exo, Ruth, Psa, Pro, and Jonah [mna] -Papua New Guinea 1996 (DBL 2015) 
\h 3 Yoan 
\toc1 Ro Ki Yoan Ta Iwe Tel Pa 
\toc2 3 Yoan 
\toc3 3Yo 
\mt1 Ro Ki Yoan Ta Iwe Tel Pa  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1-2 O Gaius, nio ta aŋwe mboroŋan pa lupŋana ki Krisi, ta aŋbeede ro ti ima pu.  
\p Pa sua ŋonoono ta ilup ti, mi leleŋ pu ilip kat. Tanata aŋzuŋzuŋ Anutu be iziiri mete ma imbot molo pu, mibe ipombol uraata ku ta boozomen ma iloondo ambai men, kembei ta kunum tomini imbot ambai. Ŋonoono.   
\p
\v 3 Toŋmatiziŋ kiti pakan timar mi tisotaara yo pa urum kembei nu kiskis kat sua ŋonoono mi toto ka mbulu. Tana aŋleŋ na, ikam yo ma leleŋ ambai kat.  
\v 4 Pa sombe aŋleŋ kembei lutuŋ bizin ta aŋpaute zin pa Yesu na titoto sua ŋonoono ka mbulu, ina ta ikam yo ma leleŋ ambai ma ilip. Koroŋ toro sa irao ikam yo ma leleŋ ambai ta kembei na som.   
\p
\v 5 O tiziŋ, uraata ku ta kampewe zin toŋmatiziŋ kiti, ina nu motom zze pa mi kamam kat. Ŋonoono, zin pakan na, nu ute zin som. Pa zin kar toro. Tamen tima tipet ku na, nu motom pizin mi mboro kat zin.  
\v 6 Kampeŋana ku tana, nio aŋute paso, wal tana tomtom kizin pakan timar mi tiso urum lela lupŋana tiam mi amleŋ. Wal ta kembei, sombe timaŋga mini pa pai, na ambai be re zin pa koroŋ pakan. Mi so uulu zin, na uulu kat zin. Pa ina, zin tikam Anutu ruŋguunu ma timar.\x + \xo 1:6 \xt  Tit 3:13\x*  
\v 7 Wal ta kembei, zin tizem kar kizin sorok na som. Tikam pa Krisi zaana tau. Mi zin tikamam kadoono sa la kizin matan munŋan som.\x + \xo 1:7 \xt  Mt 10:8; Ŋgo 20:33,35\x*  
\v 8 Tana iti lende uraata be takam zin wal ta kembei mi tu'uulu zin. Naso itiŋan takam uraata pa sua ŋonoono.   
\s1 Mbulu sananŋana ki Diotrepes  
\p
\v 9 Muŋgu nio aŋbeede sua pakan pa lupŋana tiom. Tamen Diotrepes ta iserseere be iwe mataana pa lupŋana tiom na, ni itit yam mi ileŋ la kalŋoyam som.  
\v 10 Tana kaimer, sombe aŋma aŋlou yom, tona aŋswe mbulu kini ta boozomen ma ipet mat. Pa ni ininin kao piam, mi iyyo kwoono piam pa sua sananŋan boozomen. Mi ikamam mbulu tina men som. Pa ikamam zin toŋmatiziŋ kiti ma tilala ruumu kini som. Mi zin wal pakan ta tisombe tikam zin, to ni ipetekewe zin, mi iser zin pa lupŋana ki Krisi ma timbot mat.   
\s1 Mbulu ambaiŋana ki Demitrius  
\p
\v 11 O tiziŋ, mbulu sananŋana ta kembena na, to pepe. Kam mbulu ambaiŋana men. Pa sombe tomtom sa ikamam mbulu kini ma ambai men, ina ni Anutu tomtom kini. Mi sombe tomtom sa inoknok sanaana kamŋana, na ni iute Anutu som.\x + \xo 1:11 \xt  Mbo 37:27; 1Pe 3:11; 1Yo 3:6+\x*   
\p
\v 12 Mi Demitrius na, wal boozomen tiwidit uruunu. Pa mbulu kini indeŋdeeŋe men pa sua ŋonoono. Mi niam tomini amwidit uruunu. Mi nu ute: Sua tiam, ina ŋonoono men.   
\s1 Sua pemetŋana  
\p
\v 13 Nio motoŋ iŋgalŋgal sua boozomen tabe aŋso piom. Tamen leleŋ be aŋbeede se ro pepe.  
\v 14 Pa iŋgi aŋur motoŋ be molo som, to aŋma aŋre yom. Tonabe itiŋan taparre iti mi toso lende sua.   
\p
\v 15 Merere ko imboro u ma mbot ambai men. Ŋonoono.  
\p Toŋmatiziŋ pakan ta niamŋan ambotmbot i, tikam aigule kizin pu. Mi nu ta kembena, kam aigule tiam pizin toŋmatiziŋ kiti ta niomŋan kombotmbot na. Sinin zin ma timap.   